{"tid":425672,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"GUNDAM BUILD 高達創戰者 對戰紀錄 第三話","createTime":"2017-10-06T02:33:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-27T10:38:41.000Z","uid":30745,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"b52cdf705e46bb810de7911aea37fee483778aaa","tid":425672,"uid":30745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T02:33:39.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/05/172126_27f4041f76b12dc7f1c25214dfdce52e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F05%2F172126_27f4041f76b12dc7f1c25214dfdce52e.jpg&h=468258f8&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[故事大綱]<br />\n<br />\n為了打倒邪惡《宮賀》，超級文奈與超級強子靠著北宋之地圖前往那座城池。穿過陰暗的森林之後，出現在文奈等人眼前的，是一群小熊霸在悠閒地生活的熊熊村。可是小熊霸不知為何一發現文奈與強子之後，就驚慌失措地逃去了。兩人還沒弄清楚這是什麼情況，充滿敵意的智奈熊霸就出現在面前。<br />\n<br />\n官網：<a href=\"http://hk.gundam.info/topics/white/139664?region=all&amp;cat=&amp;bigcat=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.gundam.info%2Ftopics%2Fwhite%2F139664%3Fregion%3Dall%26cat%3D%26bigcat%3D&d=JuMPYOSyz7EowLnPmpXzyU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=6a9994f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.gundam.info/topics/white/139664?region=all&amp;cat=&amp;bigcat=</a>"},{"pid":"45851f5e142aa3190a5cd918f1e5e71b5f459143","tid":425672,"uid":34197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T02:36:41.000Z","msg":"強子左胸好大粒lin餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"567c3c47de912b0f9cd35997b6dd9cc5a6c13bb4","tid":425672,"uid":128287,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T02:41:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>強子左胸好大粒lin餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n果個位應該係大魔發射散光整盲人用, but放係個波度就......"},{"pid":"fe5b294d668de7155dd9116f560e3593bd177492","tid":425672,"uid":30745,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T03:05: